WorkItem.Description:
I upgraded to 1.7.1 and noticed that these Page Setup parameters are now initialized as true. When I needed to set the page width to 1 (without setting the page height) I used to do:
 
     $objPageSetup->setFitToWidth(1);
 
While now it's required to do:
 
     $objPageSetup->setFitToWidth(1);
     $objPageSetup->setFitToHeight(0);
 
Might be a good idea to mention this in the documentation, as previous versions behaved differently.
